Alembic migrations for the SportsLab API.

- Run from monorepo root:
    uv run alembic -c apps/api/alembic.ini upgrade head
- Generate a new revision from ORM diff:
    uv run alembic -c apps/api/alembic.ini revision -m "description" --autogenerate
- Downgrade one step:
    uv run alembic -c apps/api/alembic.ini downgrade -1

The database URL is read from the ``SPORTSLAB_DATABASE_URL`` environment
variable (see ``apps/api/src/api/config.py``). If unset, migrations run
against ``sqlite:///./local.db`` as a dev convenience. CI / prod deploys
always set the env var explicitly.
